serious efforts for social and economic reforms which "would
ultimately bring prosperity and progress to the country".
</P>
<P>
Inaugurating the new terminal building at Sukkur Airport in
Sindh province, Sharif deplored that he had launched a number of
major projects during his previous tenure from 1990-1993 but they
were abandoned by the following Benazir Bhutto government.
</P>
<P>
