initiated in 1992 and should have been completed in 1994, he said,
adding that for its own reasons the Benazir government withheld
this vital project of the area.
</P>
<P>
However, it was his government which again started the work on
this project and it has now been completed, said Sharif.
</P>
<P>
Answering questions from media, Sharif said that his government
was "intact and strong" and that efforts to destabilize his
government would not succeed.
</P>
<P>
