Regional Workshop for Parliamentarians on Reproductive Health and
Legislation, was officially opened by Ugandan President Yoweri
Museveni.
</P>
<P>
It will focus on the poor reproductive health in the region
and seek legal ways to protect rights of women.
</P>
<P>
