<HEADLINE> Fixtures for Asian Men's Volleyball Olympic Qualification </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 27 (Xinhua) -- Following is the schedule,
issued by Asian Volleyball Confederation here on Monday, for the
Asian men's volleyball 2000 Olympic qualifying tournament to be
held in Shanghai, China, in December:
</P>
<P>
On 27th, China vs Japan, Chinese Taipei vs South Korea;
</P>
<P>
On 28th, Japan vs South Korea, China vs Chinese Taipei;
</P>
<P>
On 29th, China vs South Korea, Chinese Taipei vs Japan.
</P>
<P>
The winner of the tournament will represent Asia to take part
in the 2000 Sydney Olympics. 
