<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, September 27 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 6,092.78 points on Monday,
down 86.49 points, or 1.40 percent, from Friday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was active with the turnover reaching over 82
trillion Turkish Liras (over 178 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 125.56 points, or 1.54 percent, to
close at 7,728.77 points, the industrial index fell 49.79 points,
or 1.07 points, to close at 4,584.77 points and the services
index went down 109.17 points, or 1.63 percent, to close at
6,600.78 points. 
</P>
