China's modernization drive.
</P>
<P>
Painting a rosy picture for China's IT market, Wu Jichuan,
Minister of Information Industry, said the mobile phone users will
increase from the present 36 million to 100 million by 2003. He
said China is also expected to have about 20 million Internet
users, up from four million at present.
</P>
<P>
