Liberation:
</P>
<P>
-- After being criticized for powerlessness in front of the
plan by tire group Michelin to lay off 7,500 workers, French Prime
Minister Lionel Jospin will reaffirm on Monday the position of his
leftwing government on employment at a meeting of Socialist
deputies in Strasbourg.
</P>
