stage rocket over Japan in August last year. The DPRK said it was
launching a satellite, but Tokyo insists it was for testing a
medium-range ballistic missile.
</P>
<P>
Japan's sanctions include a freeze on food aid and charter
flights between the two nations. Japan also suspended negotiations
on normalizing diplomatic ties with DPRK.
