<P>
 It took only three years for the Inner Mongolia Autonomous
Region after its founding to check the spread of the plague. The
Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region controlled the spread of the plague
in 1963. In 1961, smallpox was eliminated throughout the whole
country, including minority areas. The life span of Tibetans has
increased to 65 years from 36 in 1959, the year the democratic
